Well, as future“Chief Election Officer” of Arizona, let me tell you what the Secretary ofStates are trying to do, in almost unison, to squash election integrity. Theexplicit goal of the NASS Task Force on Vote Verification was to ensure thatnothing like “a Maricopa-Style Forensic Audit would ever happen again.” Why? Election officials should be able totrack the movement and transport of ballots, voting machines, and otherelection materials through witnesses, signature logs, security seals, video,etc. A break in the chain of custody increases the risk that the integrity orreliability of the asset cannot be restored.
